<!--
`optarg_delimiter` contains the delimiter (either " " or "=")
consistently used by `long_option` and/or `vms_option` elements with
option arguments, or "mixed" if delimiter usage is mixed (both " " and
"=" used). If no such options exist, no `optarg_delimiter` attribute
will be present. `short_option` elements may only use spaces as
opt/arg delimiters; they don't affect the attribute.
-->
